articles.title: Military ties top agenda as Biden meets Philippines’ Marcos Jr - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Leaders to agree to greater US-Philippines military coordination, officials say, amid rising tensions in Asia Pacific.
articles.content: United States President Joe Biden and his Philippines counterpart Ferdinand Marcos Jr are set to agree on new guidelines to strengthen military cooperation, US officials said, as the two leaders meet… [+5611 chars]
